comment: This app uses your device's camera, meaning that if it is taking too long to scan, your camera is probably not in focus. This app can only see through your camera but not adjust its settings so if your scan is really slow or not working, open up your camera, put it at the same proximity as you would scan, tap the center of the screen, and that will focus your camera. Then re-open the scanner and scan away.
